========
selenium
========

Installing the testing tool.
I intend to use the selenium RC test tool
This is a java-based server that sits on the test machine, and sends commands
to the javascript based app on the browser.  The server interprets commands sent to it, over the network, by a client, which can be python



cp selenium.py /usr/local/lib/python2.6/site-packages/
cp selenium.py /usr/local/lib/python2.6/dist-packages/ #this works - dunno



